Successor -> Refer the picture, 16 successor is 30

Logic --> go to the right, loop it's till left  leaf node.. refer the below logic


Successor(Node node)
{
    if (node == null) return null;
    Node currentNode = node.right;
    while(currentNode!=null){
    currentNode = currentNode.left;
}

return currentNode; // Successor of the given Node;


}